longBusinessSummary: Vital Healthcare Property Trust is an NZX-listed fund that invests in high-quality healthcare properties in New Zealand and Australia including private hospitals (~80%* of portfolio value), ambulatory care facilities (~16%* of portfolio value) and aged care (~4%* of portfolio value). Vital is the leading specialist listed landlord of healthcare property in Australasia. Vital is managed by Northwest Healthcare Properties Management Limited, a subsidiary of Toronto Stock Exchange listed Northwest Healthcare Properties REIT, a global owner and manager of healthcare property.
